{"tid":1680832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊偉雄稱20支損毀智慧燈柱回復照明　將配合5G發展","createTime":"2019-10-29T05:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T06:06:22.000Z","uid":180902,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c4347a9e8132642cc1921d1bf99e50b5e4b5aa03","tid":1680832,"uid":180902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:03:05.000Z","msg":"在立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會會議，創新及科技局局長楊偉雄解釋有關新一份施政報告的創科政策。經民聯議員盧偉國關注最近有智慧燈柱被破壞，反映有市民不明白政府推行大數據的政策。創新及科技局局長楊偉雄表示，發展智能燈柱的所有程序會在陽光下進行，所有安裝過程也經過區議會認可，局方最近已引入第三方專家意見審視，未來會更加公開貼地諮詢公眾。 他又說，留意到有20支智慧燈柱損毀，現已回復照明功能，未來會繼續配合5G發展，例如收集環保方面的數據。<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-29 12:58:42<br />\nSource :RTHK"},{"pid":"0240dea84ce9244f8c69aa1becde415ddfd03a0e","tid":1680832,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bcd0ce6548d38af0cff2952b7cdbfd604bf15923","tid":1680832,"uid":189430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾陽痿雄連搵LINK睇波都唔識<br />\n我實信你識乜撚野叫5G啦屌你老母<br />\n都俾人拆穿哂支野入面有D咩野架啦<br />\n仲係度扮撚哂野話唔關事,無恥到你咁撚樣真係未撚見過<br />\n祝你快D落去搵STEVE JOB,不過人地想唔撚想見到你係另一回事啦屌"},{"pid":"112c4206416b202e844ac89ae7f41e1fdc4661f1","tid":1680832,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:09:55.000Z","msg":"創科局長連上網都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf328919c71a8e13dbbfa6c555cf22ba2